                <p>Let's start with a clear and honest statement: <strong>Zapier is a fantastic tool</strong>. Along with other no-code platforms like Make.com, it has revolutionized how small businesses operate. These tools are like the first employee you ever hired—a multi-talented generalist who single-handedly took a mountain of manual work off your plate. They democratized automation, allowing non-technical founders to connect their apps and build simple workflows without writing a single line of code.</p>

